{"tid":656382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東孫子公開露面根本不像！ 網民質疑是替身","createTime":"2018-05-07T08:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T13:47:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd37c167b2b66fed79f05d04739047d36f4bfef","tid":656382,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/161143_1600dbd40c86e24702fb09cc0c64e822.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F161143_1600dbd40c86e24702fb09cc0c64e822.png&h=92d9afcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/161155_20e20ea6dae222be528a587ffcc4ecd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F161155_20e20ea6dae222be528a587ffcc4ecd3.png&h=57025eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國前領導人毛澤東孫子、現任解放軍少將毛新宇，日前傳出在北韓重大車禍中喪命，隨後毛家人否認此事，毛新宇如今更公開露面拍照，但大批網民懷疑照片中的人根本就不是本人。<br />\n綜合中媒報導，中國船舶工業系統工程研究院與軍事科學院戰爭研究院，於5月4日舉行協同創新研討會，期間戰爭研究院黨委常委毛新宇、佟海青、陳榮弟、聶送等人前來參觀實驗室，並在座談會上致詞。<br />\n從現場合照中可以看到，站在照片左一的毛新宇公開面對鏡頭，不過有網民直言，「平心而論，左一這個胖子長得不太像宇哥。」還有人附和地說「我也這麼認為，而且就他還特別模糊。」一名網友則表示，「這是我見過最不清楚的微博照片，此地無銀一千三百兩。」<br />\n一位網民突破盲點地說，再怎麼說毛將軍應該要站在中間才對，怎麼會站到左一去？其他人則解答「中間不太好P（修圖），放旁邊比較方便。」還有人諷刺地說，「雖然沒有遇難，但連五官都撞到不認得了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2417193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2417193&d=PipUh5SrMdnZYIP%2FzYps9E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c2a3a2c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2417193&h=b163ff30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2417193</a>"},{"pid":"9be695b7b14e56587a72f910fd5c7695f102e96b","tid":656382,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"},{"pid":"8ed78c1675a84e33a98ef0a65ad2af47a183a04d","tid":656382,"uid":62599,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"孫子也是假的"},{"pid":"6e794d4358f16962724893669f676cf7061f1b1e","tid":656382,"uid":8048,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"中國只有騙子才是真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11871ebc9e20eb7c91037e11af681d34d1ab5693","tid":656382,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"死了"},{"pid":"f3d860501747e7c52ec8a4e5e299ebb8eeabd5a1","tid":656382,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"molamola 真係死咗喇"},{"pid":"4190a4faf08e82511f26534fe2c64ffda6e2f1a5","tid":656382,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"啲大陸仔咁夠薑"},{"pid":"8e1b987a7214c3d1fadbc1aba17d126111686e3c","tid":656382,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"朝巴士墮橋36死包括32華客　金正恩探望傷者<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkncn-20180423112241778-0423_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180423%2Fbkncn-20180423112241778-0423_05011_001.html&d=PipUh5SrMdnZYIP%2FzYps9E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bd49a0a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bkncn-20180423112241778-0423_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞解碼：北韓多爛路　車禍路段屬品質最佳<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180423/bknint-20180423140340892-0423_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2F